description:
This week, Cody's going to do something a bit different. We get quite a few emails from his fans wanting to know what his workout routine is, so Cody decided to give you a taste of his iron pumping.

But don't worry, there's still an orgasmic ending when the hunk kicks back on the chest machine and milks his Italian sausage.

Enjoy!
title: Buffing lesson, all muscles are involved!
